    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely grate your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>parsley</strong> and <strong>coriander</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Peel and finely dice your <strong>shallot[s]</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>diced shallot</strong> to a small bowl with your <strong>red wine vinegar</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>sugar </strong>and set aside to pickle – this is your <strong>quick-pickled shallot</strong></p>",
