    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the chicken is cooking, chop your <strong>tomato[es]</strong> finely</p><p>Dice your <strong>cucumber </strong>finely</p><p>Wash your <strong>lettuce</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper and shred finely</p>",
