    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the brown rice is cooked and slightly cooled, add the <strong>chopped tomato</strong>, <strong>diced cucumber </strong>and <strong>shredded lettuce </strong>to the pot with the <strong>chimichurri-style sauce</strong></p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and give everything a good mix up, reserve the bowl – this is your <strong>chimichurri-style brown rice salad</strong></p>",
