      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>remaining grated garlic </strong>(not a big garlic fan? Try using less!) to the reserved bowl with your <strong>natural yoghurt</strong>, <strong>remaining chopped herbs </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper </strong>– this is your <strong>garlic yoghurt</strong></p>",
